Tue Nov 14 18:42:18 UTC 2006  Iliyan Jeliazkov  <iliyan@ociweb.com>

        * ace/Service_Gestalt.inl:
        * ace/Service_Gestalt.cpp:

          After a gestalt gets close()-ed it is still a valid instance
          however, because it is disassociated from its service repository
          the situation becomes another special case the gestalt
          implementation must account for.  This change is in addition to
          the bug fix introduced with the change from "Thu Nov 9 20:07:42
          UTC 2006".

Tue Nov 14 14:30:12 UTC 2006  Johnny Willemsen  <jwillemsen@remedy.nl>

