        * ace/Service_Config.cpp:
        * ace/Service_Gestalt.h:
        * ace/Service_Gestalt.cpp:

          A follow up to my change from "Wed Nov 8 22:12:46". Adding the
          close_svcs() call in ACE_Service_Config::close() ensured that
          the repository and its contents gets properly finalized, but it
          did not account for the potential subsequent re-opening of the
          Service Config. This causes failures in open/close/open
          scenarios, like Framework_Component_Test.

