Mon Oct 30 17:23:15 UTC 2006  Steve Huston  <shuston@riverace.com>

        * include/makeinclude/wrapper_macros.GNU: Added 2 new build options,
          dmalloc and mtrace. When specified at build time (e.g. make mtrace=1)
          the PLATFORM_DMALLOC_CPPFLAGS and/or PLATFORM_MTRACE_CPPFLAGS values
          are added to CPPFLAGS. For dmalloc, the PLATFORM_DMALLOC_LDFLAGS and
          PLATFORM_DMALLOC_LIBS are added to LDFLAGS and LIBS, respectively.
          Also added the ability to specify additional purify and quantify
          command-line options by setting PLATFORM_PURIFY_OPTIONS and
          PLATFORM_QUANTIFY_OPTIONS, respectively. Thank you to Howard
          Finer for supplying these additions.

